{"word":"G3512 - νεωτερικός - neōterikós - neh-o-ter'-ik-os - Youthful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νεωτερικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">neōterikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">neh-o-ter'-ik-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Youthful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாலியத்திற்குரிய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"peculiar to the age of youth, youthful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the compound of <a href=\"#/G3501 - νέος - néos - neh'-os/3501\">G3501</a>; <i>appertaining to younger</i> persons, that is, <i>juvenile:</i> - youthful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3494/3494\">G3494</a>, <a href=\"#/G3495/3495\">G3495</a>, <a href=\"#/G3512/3512\">G3512</a>"}]}